        <p class="lead font-serif text-xl">For the discerning traveler, extraordinary culinary experiences transcend mere sustenance—they become profound cultural immersions, sensory adventures, and memories that linger long after the last bite. From remote mountaintop restaurants to centuries-old dining traditions, these are the gastronomic journeys that justify planning an entire itinerary around a single meal.</p>
        
